{"tid":746719,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKUSPACE PLK Q&A] 讀Hotel Man的過來人「你問我答」","createTime":"2018-07-17T19:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T02:54:05.000Z","uid":164249,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25de1f9620a1227fd25a438e8b8e9def8da0e7e2","tid":746719,"uid":164249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T19:22:02.000Z","msg":"一講讀hotel man個個淨係會諗起hkcc...<br />\n不過個人覺得asso⋯⋯冇信心入返U都係唔好讀<br />\n所以放榜個日走左去九龍灣太空即場報呢個high dip course然後就收左<br />\n感覺收生都幾求其<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過讀完覺得其實呢間太空嘅親戚都唔錯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開學第一感覺係設施唔錯，有一層酒店管理培訓中心幾新幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係個到上堂心情都靚啲<br />\n學嘅野general d but 多d可以樣樣都識啲<br />\nSem 1 gpa出左自己都嚇醒<br />\n完全冇諗過自己會有機入返U<br />\n之後keep住都ok<br />\n不過其中有個sem係淨出placement<br />\n所以overall 3個sem定生死都幾肉緊<br />\n諗起placement都又喊又笑<br />\n超攰超多野做超大壓力（U interview 同placement重疊），但係啲同事好笑又好玩又好包容我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完左placement可以轉full time/casual staff<br />\n畢業之後都唔休搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瞓唔著屎忽痕嚟分享下<br />\n有咩問題都可以問我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd1929c75273894077eacfe7a5408fa4dd2a55e","tid":746719,"uid":147272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T18:07:37.000Z","msg":"Gpa？"},{"pid":"e62612132f39d409b1434905e2bda294d6ed0cff","tid":746719,"uid":164249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd1929c75273894077eacfe7a5408fa4dd2a55e","tid":746719,"uid":147272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T18:07:37.000Z","msg":"Gpa？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"3.63 grad"},{"pid":"37913bad6831ca288b565574defaeea243f39c7b","tid":746719,"uid":10210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:34:51.000